This is the finest Coffe shop in all of Williamsburg- bar none. The owner is knowledgable, dedicated to creating the highest quality in taste and experience, and truly cares about you as a customer. If you want a place to relax, study, chat, break the ice or dump your girlfriend - this is the place for you. The Coffe is the best in the neighborhood (beating out blue bottle and Oslo for all their expensive cat-poo beans) and the hand crafted ambiance is like a sanctuary to a tired soul. If you want a gross bathroom and burnt soup- go to Starbucks. If you want fresh made treats and the best dam cup this side of the river- Northerly Coffe.
